# Bench artifacts — regenerated per run, host-specific, never commit.
Benchmarks/results/
Benchmarks/Tooling/cpp-bench/build/
Benchmarks/Tooling/clickhouse-cpp/
Benchmarks/Tooling/redis-cpp/
Benchmarks/Tooling/jsonschema-go/

